<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Access Request</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Access Request</h1>
    <p>Hello {{ name }},</p>
    <p>You have received a request for access from {{ requesterName }}. They are requesting permission to access your information.</p>
    <p>If you grant permission, please provide them with the access code: {{ link }}</p>
    <p>Thank you!</p>
</body>
</html>
